card.city

Class CityAreaCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • card.city.CityAreaCard

  • public class CityAreaCard
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a wrapper around the board areas to hold the state of a city card.
    City cards belong to players and can be played once per round (except for AnkhMorporkArea.SMALL_GODS. So we need to keep track of that "played" vs. "not played" state.
    Version:
    2.0
    Author:
    Team 10 - SOEN6441
